# Production build (used by `vite build` in the Docker frontend-build stage).
# On Hugging Face the frontend and FastAPI backend are served from the SAME
# origin (port 7860), so all /api/* calls and the /ws WebSocket resolve against
# this URL. This overrides frontend/.env (which targets localhost for dev).
#
# NOTE: this is the public URL of the HF Space. If the Space is renamed, update it.
VITE_API_BASE=https://yourgrimreaper-energy-dashboard.hf.space
